at has been crafted with years of experience. Wave is built to last and give you the best experience possible.</p></div></div><div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-sky-500/10"><div class="absolute -right-20 -top-20 h-[200px] w-[200px] rounded-full bg-sky-500/20 blur-[80px] transition-all duration-500 group-hover:bg-sky-500/30"></div><div class="relative z-10"><div class="mb-6 flex items-start justify-between"><div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white/5 text-sky-400 ring-1 ring-white/10 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-sky-500 group-hover:text-white group-hover:shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-sky-500/30"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-cloud h-6 w-6" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17.5 19H9a7 7 0 1 1 6.71-9h1.79a4.5 4.5 0 1 1 0 9Z"></path></svg></div><span class="rounded-full border border-white/5 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 backdrop-blur-md transition-colors group-hover:border-sky-500/30 group-hover:text-sky-300">Integrated API</span></div><h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-white transition-colors group-hover:text-sky-200">Cloud Script Hub</h3><p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-300">You are able to search for any script you desire, for any game possible, powered by ScriptBlox, it is all integrated into Wave for your convenience.</p></div></div><div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-sky-500/10"><div class="absolute -right-20 -top-20 h-[200px] w-[200px] rounded-full bg-sky-500/20 blur-[80px] transition-all duration-500 group-hover:bg-sky-500/30"></div><div class="relative z-10"><div class="mb-6 flex items-start justify-between"><div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white/5 text-sky-400 ring-1 ring-white/10 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-sky-500 group-hover:text-white group-hover:shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-sky-500/30"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-code-xml h-6 w-6" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m18 16 4-4-4-4"></path><path d="m6 8-4 4 4 4"></path><path d="m14.5 4-5 16"></path></svg></div><span class="rounded-full border border-white/5 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 backdrop-blur-md transition-colors group-hover:border-sky-500/30 group-hover:text-sky-300">Readable Output</span></div><h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-white transition-colors group-hover:text-sky-200">Decompiler</h3><p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-300">Readable script decompiler for inspecting code, reverse engineering and debugging. Wave allows you to explore every single script possible.</p></div></div><div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-sky-500/10"><div class="absolute -right-20 -top-20 h-[200px] w-[200px] rounded-full bg-sky-500/20 blur-[80px] transition-all duration-500 group-hover:bg-sky-500/30"></div><div class="relative z-10"><div class="mb-6 flex items-start justify-between"><div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white/5 text-sky-400 ring-1 ring-white/10 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-sky-500 group-hover:text-white group-hover:shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-sky-500/30"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-headphones h-6 w-6" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 14h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-7a9 9 0 0 1 18 0v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-1a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3"></path></svg></div><span class="rounded-full border border-white/5 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 backdrop-blur-md transition-colors group-hover:border-sky-500/30 group-hover:text-sky-300">Always On</span></div><h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-white transition-colors group-hover:text-sky-200">24/7 Support</h3><p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-300">A dedicated support team and Discord presence that actually responds, no matter what time zone you&#x27;re in. We&#x27;re here to help every user!</p></div></div><div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] p-8 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-sky-500/10"><div class="absolute -right-20 -top-20 h-[200px] w-[200px] rounded-full bg-sky-500/20 blur-[80px] transition-all duration-500 group-hover:bg-sky-500/30"></div><div class="relative z-10"><div class="mb-6 flex items-start justify-between"><div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white/5 text-sky-400 ring-1 ring-white/10 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-sky-500 group-hover:text-white group-hover:shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-sky-500/30"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-server h-6 w-6" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="20" height="8" x="2" y="2" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><rect width="20" height="8" x="2" y="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="6" x2="6.01" y1="6" y2="6"></line><line x1="6" x2="6.01" y1="18" y2="18"></line></svg></div><span class="rounded-full border border-white/5 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 backdrop-blur-md transition-colors group-hover:border-sky-500/30 group-hover:text-sky-300">Always Ready</span></div><h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-bold text-white transition-colors group-hover:text-sky-200">No Downtime</h3><p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-300">Wave has had zero downtime since its initial release. Our reliable infrastructure ensures that Wave is available, whenever you need it. (with compensations on downtime).</p></div></div></section></div><div class="mt-32"><div class="my-12 flex items-center gap-4 md:my-16"><div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-slate-500/40 to-transparent"></div><span class="text-[0.68rem] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-slate-300/80">Plans</span><div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-slate-500/40 to-transparent"></div></div><section class="relative"><div class="mb-16 text-center"><h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white sm:text-4xl">Simple, Transparent Pricing</h2><p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-400">Choose the perfect plan for your needs. No hidden fees.</p></div><div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4"><div class="group relative flex flex-col rounded-2xl border p-6 transition-all duration-300 border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] hover:border-white/10 hover:bg-white/[0.04]"><div class="mb-8"><h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400">Daily</h3><div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-1"><span class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">$2.49</span><span class="text-sm text-slate-500">/ <!-- -->24 Hours</span></div></div><ul class="mb-8 space-y-4 